root.data:
Aviation

Every year by the fall data for the previous year is available to ICAO Member States at a country level.

Road/Rail/Inland waterways/Pipelines

Data are collected for the reference year starting in September of the following year, and are typically published by the following January. So year-2 data were published in Januaryyear-1.
